Name: Juggernaut
FlavourText: What divides the conqueror \r\n from the conquered? Perseverance.

Name: Berserker
FlavourText: The savage path is \r\nalways swift and sure.

Name: Chieftain
FlavourText: The Ancestors speak \r\nthrough your clenched fists.

Name: Raider
FlavourText: No hunt is complete without\r\nthe gutting and the skinning.

Name: Deadeye
FlavourText: A woman can change the world \r\nwith a single well-placed arrow.

Name: Pathfinder
FlavourText: There are venoms and virtues aplenty in \r\n the wilds, if you know where to look.

Name: Occultist
FlavourText: Throw off the chains\r\nof fear and embrace that\r\n which was forbidden.

Name: Elementalist
FlavourText: Feed a storm with savage intent \r\nand not even the strongest walls\r\nwill hold it back.

Name: Necromancer
FlavourText: Embrace the serene\r\npower that is undeath.

Name: Slayer
FlavourText: No judge. No jury.\r\nJust the executioner.

Name: Gladiator
FlavourText: Raise your hand to the \r\nroaring crowd and pledge \r\nyour allegiance to glory.

Name: Champion
FlavourText:
Champion that which 
 you love. He who fights
 for nothing, dies
 for nothing.

Name: Inquisitor
FlavourText: Truth is elusive, yet God has\r\nprovided us with all the tools \r\n necessary to find it.

Name: Hierophant
FlavourText: Drink deeply from God's\r\n chalice, for the faithful\r\n will never find it empty.

Name: Guardian
FlavourText: When bound by faith\r\n and respect, the flock\r\n will overwhelm the wolf.

Name: Assassin
FlavourText: Death is a banquet. \r\n It's up to the murderer \r\n to write the menu.

Name: Trickster
FlavourText: Everyone knows how to die. \r\n Some just need a little nudge \r\nto get them started.

Name: Saboteur
FlavourText: The artist need not be present \r\n to make a lasting impression.
